    "page": 1,
    "title": "4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions",
    "article": "\n<p>While the initial cost of dental implants is higher than regular dentures, their longevity and contribution to optimal oral health make them worthwhile. Here, we introduce four relatively affordable dental implants. Let's take a look!</p>\n<img alt=\"4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 2,
    "title": "4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions",
    "article": "\n<h4>1. Snap-On Dentures</h4>\n<img alt=\"4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Snap-on dentures are an alternative to traditional implants and a more comfortable and practical option compared to removable dentures. They are more affordable as the cost is calculated per implant. Additionally, this technology can reduce the risk of jawbone shrinkage and facial collapse.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 3,
    "title": "4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions",
    "article": "\n<h4>2. Mini Implants</h4>\n<img alt=\"4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Mini implants, due to their smaller diameter, cost about half as much as standard dental implants. The procedure for mini implants is simpler and the recovery time is quicker.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 4,
    "title": "4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions",
    "article": "\n<h4>3. Implant Overdentures</h4>\n<img alt=\"4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_4.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_4.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Implant overdentures, also called implant-supported dentures, are safer than mini implants and snap-on dentures, yet not as expensive since they are also priced per implant. Implants help maintain the integrity of your jawbone.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 5,
    "title": "4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions",
    "article": "\n<h4>4. All-On-4 Implants</h4>\n<img alt=\"4 Affordable Dental Implant Solutions_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions/4-affordable-dental-implant-solutions_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>All-on-4 provides a comprehensive solution for patients with reduced jawbone density. It involves placing four angled implants in the denser posterior part of the jawbone. This ensures your new smile looks more natural.</p>\n</img>"
  }
]